creator: BeatFun
descriptionHtml:
Try great time killer game now! Beat Smash combines one-finger control gameplay with beautiful music and gun sounds, help you relaxing and feeling comfortable.

How to play:
- Block tiles come with EDM music.
- Break the tiles by sliding your finger exactly.
- Do not miss any tiles to keep the game going.
- Each song has been designed with addictive challenges, enjoy it!
- Collect coins for unlocking new songs.

Game Features:
- Fantastic EDM music and gun-sound effects.
- Easy to play, one-finger control.
- Cool Skins and Weapons for you select.

If you are not steady, don't play it, you will be addicted it 😊
If any producer or label has an issue with any of the music used in the game, please send email to us and it will be deleted immediately if necessary.

Contact us:
Are you having problems? Please send an email to beatfunvn@outlook.com

Try great time killer game now! Beat Shoot 3D: Fnf music game combines one-finger control gameplay with beautiful music and gun sounds, help you relaxing and feeling comfortable.

How to play:
- Block tiles come with EDM music.
- Break the tiles by sliding your finger exactly.
- Do not miss any tiles to keep the game going.
- Each song has been designed with addictive challenges, enjoy it!
- Collect coins for unlocking new songs.

Game Features:
- FNF Story mode challenge characters to rescue your girlfriend.
- Play with friends or online player around the world.
- Upload own songs from your music library.
- Fantastic EDM music and gun-sound effects.
- Easy to play, one-finger control.
- Cool Skins and Weapons for you select.

If you are not steady, don't play it, you will be addicted it 😊
If any producer or label has an issue with any of the music used in the game, please send email to us and it will be deleted immediately if necessary.

Contact us:
Are you having problems? Please send an email to beatfunvn@outlook.com
